{"tid":924210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完去日本個個post 啱啱比鬼壓","createTime":"2018-12-02T02:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T03:01:12.000Z","uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe72b8cf9ec81c83a00fe2d03609fd2745d28c5","tid":924210,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:20:42.000Z","msg":"首先我用左個比教薑硬動作訓 ，無話特登<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我終於知比鬼壓點黎<br />\n<br />\n只要你半訓半醒個下<br />\n<br />\n開眼之後，選擇合埋眼繼續訓，咁你身體就順便無事，因為我成日都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n但係我睇完個post有少少驚，就開始驚，開始想郁，仲會ff左好多野，但同自己講唔好驚，手腳郁唔到，頭頂仲會好似有力量壓住你咁，<br />\n想叫貓貓過黎都叫唔到。<br />\n<br />\n之後有鬼壓床之前我發左個春夢，姐係發夢翻左去中學，同個唔識既女仔，可能隔離post影響，個女仔我未見過，之後出現係我夢裡面，<br />\n佢又挨住我膊頭，我同佢好sweet 。<br />\n<br />\n因為我想繼續發所以再訓 之後就鬼壓床<br />\n<br />\n鬼壓床你愈驚，身體就愈麻。"},{"pid":"1b439d6305da5684b8d11ad95a9b96851f617598","tid":924210,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:26:46.000Z","msg":"立即落樓<br />\n唔好係連登到"},{"pid":"50a24e448f2bc9a4e26a0e8b30eb4044ece53fdf","tid":924210,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8801ddcddf5e2d88369962511b1bf70fa37b789","tid":924210,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:38:39.000Z","msg":"睡眠癱瘓症"},{"pid":"e01de96938a2e07761def1e2a37eb17ba7fe49a9","tid":924210,"uid":25391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"哼 嗯 哼 嗯"},{"pid":"c3c38dde3bf3d9dbc82b9568e8826701c53f8a7c","tid":924210,"uid":189911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VqUpUon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVqUpUon.jpg&h=ae695fed&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}